A gift! The beauty had given him a gift! It must mean friendship... Only friends give friends gifts. He didn't know how he knew that, but he did!<br>
<br>
Bob's eyes shone bright blue, and he stood more erect, and finally straightened his shoulders. He poked his finger into his chest. &quot;B-&quot; His mind clouded, and he looked again to his wrist. &quot;B  O  B&quot; was still carved there. He pointed to himself again. &quot;Bob.&quot; Then he pointed at the beauty, and a questioning look crossed his face. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ubellonakali.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bellona Kali</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Child of Hate</span><br>  Posts: 49<br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/12/02 5:31 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://pmp.4t.com/magelo/smallbell.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Name</span><hr size=1> Name... He wanted to know her name... <br>
