She repeated the word, not knowing what it meant, but loving it none the less. His language was breath taking, almost as stunning as he was. As'ahmay... she did not know what it meant, but for now, it would be her name. Her hand trembles at the feel of his skin against hers, another life... Interacting with another life... She knew it was all supposed to come naturally, but it didn't. Her slender finger's delicately brush away a few strands of his hair from his forehead. Everything about him so was intriguing. Entranced in his eyes she stands. As'ahmay, a new name <p><Br> <Br> <Br>I'm just a sample of a soul made to look just like a human being</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/umindles.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mindles</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Kay Oss kNite</span><br>  Posts: 41<br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/12/02 10:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: As'ahmay</span><hr size=1> Bob grabbed her hand as she lightly touched his head. As'ahmay... Beauty... He pressed her delicate hand to his cheek, reveling in the soft touch of another's skin to his own. He could remember little, though that need for remembering was rarely needed; he knew he'd never been touched with compassion so deep before this day.<br>
<br>
With her palm and fingers gingerly touching his cheek, Bob looked to As'ahmay again, lost in her perfection. He reached out and touched her cheek, and stared into her very soul. &quot;Beauty...&quot; He whispered. &quot;Mien As'ahmay... My Beauty,&quot; His hand reached slowly behind her head, and pulled her face gently closer. His lips touched hers, as he felt it should be done. When the contact was made, everything in Bob's head swam, exploded, and stole his breath away; she was so gentle...<br>
<br>
Shouts had been echoing off in the distance for nearly half an hour now, but neither had noticed, so wrapped up in each other they were. As Bob withdrew his lips, and moved closer for another wonderful kiss that filled him with so much joy, big, burly men burst through the underbrush, with tan shirts, high black boots, and big guns. &quot;As'ahmay...&quot; he whispered again. &quot;My beauty.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showMessageRange?topicID=1.topic&start=21&stop=25>2</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showPrevMessage?topicID=1.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <br><br><a self href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=20><img src=http://Auction.2y.net/user/paradisetheheretic/addreply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.emailToFriend?topicID=1.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.threadControl?topicID=1.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultima